Class DefaultParallelExecutioner

  • java.lang.Object

    public class DefaultParallelExecutioner
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParallelExecutioner
    Parallel executioner. Meant for multi threaded execution of vector and tensor operations such as dimension wise or slice wise operations.
